OL,3,CWoman, 33, who stabbed father-of-six
OL,4,Cin heart on Christmas Day jailed
OL,6,FSentencing her on Thursday, Judge Mr
OL,7,FJustice Choudhury said Carless had
OL,8,F"destroyed the life of a young man and
OL,9,Fhis family" when she fatally attacked
OL,10,Fhim at his parents' home in Elm Road,
OL,11,FNorton Canes.
